---
title: Greek-Style Chicken and Potatoes with Veggies and Feta
description: This easy Greek-inspired feast features our favourite spice, Lemon Pepper! Packed with zesty goodness, it brings a bright kick to any dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-et-pommes-de-terre-a-la-grecque-4f57c0cc.jpg
